comments: Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Lee's (GSW) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ross (ORL) cleanly intercepts the pass and keeps his foot inbounds as he passes it.
Fournier (ORL) grabs Wiggins' (GSW) arm and the contact impedes his ability to cleanly retrieve the rebound.
During the rebound, Lee (GSW) and Ross (ORL) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Carter-Williams (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position on Curry (GSW) and cleanly deflects the pass away.
Green (GSW) makes contact with Carter-Williams' (ORL) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Carter-Williams (ORL) moves laterally into Curry's (GSW) path on the drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Wiggins (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in Carter-Williams' (ORL) path and absorbs the contact.
Vucevic (ORL) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt and any marginal foot to foot contact after the release is initiated by Curry extending his leg out.
Green (GSW) briefly places two hands on Fournier (ORL) and the contact is marginal as Fournier plays through it continuing his baseline drive.
Wiggins (GSW) legally contests Vucevic's (ORL) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Curry (GSW) has his arm around Vucevic's (ORL) back and makes contact to his arm, which affects his ability to cleanly receive the pass.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in Carter-Williams' (ORL) path and absorbs the contact.
Carter-Williams (ORL) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
After the rebound, Lee (GSW) dislodges Ennis III (ORL) from his legally obtained position.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in Ennis III's (ORL) path and absorbs the contact.
